{"tid":137190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲仔無目標，無學歷做咩好","createTime":"2017-02-27T15:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T05:42:46.000Z","uid":88043,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7134f40c42c10fb9da94fad833927c3eff27b5","tid":137190,"uid":88043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"之前dse英文1左，中學畢業就出黎做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返過飲食同倉，覺得唔啱自己，唔想做成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁返左幾年工都叫有儲下錢，有廿幾萬左右嘅<br />\n不過重未諗到想做d咩，同將來會點&hellip;<br />\n屋企人就建議我讀返書，搏返個大學學位返黎，就算讀唔到出黎考海關入境都<br />\n但如果重頭黎過要由fd讀起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋都唔知揀咩科好，ive好似科科都伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個腦好亂，完全唔知自己想點<br />\n有冇巴打絲打可以俾下意見小弟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cbc924683313d73fa2d5ec92f45e3f5237d621","tid":137190,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"唔洗讀fd呀嘛？入唔入到ive hd?"},{"pid":"b0fdab2515c0fcd063b768cba95316fd5cde53f4","tid":137190,"uid":88043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗讀fd呀嘛？入唔入到ive hd?</blockquote><br />\nHd 英文1唔收喎好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487d0f9f1408935bf9b4fd1681838eac90090cab","tid":137190,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗讀fd呀嘛？入唔入到ive hd?</blockquote><br />\nHd 英文1唔收喎好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor年紀大唔知dse咩情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁可能得fd揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cb0a4ea616fee629b6381ee54099c8ea074058","tid":137190,"uid":55997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor